bibliothek.gui.dock.common.location

Class CMaximizedLocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • bibliothek.gui.dock.common.CLocation
      • bibliothek.gui.dock.common.location.AbstractStackholdingLocation
        • bibliothek.gui.dock.common.location.CMaximizedLocation

  • public class CMaximizedLocation
extends AbstractStackholdingLocation
    A location representing the maximized state. If no root-station is set, then the location of a maximized element depends on its location before maximization.
    Author:
    Benjamin Sigg
